## Post 1

**Date:** 30 June 2026

**Topic:** Embracing uncertainty when building a business

### Summary
Mark reflects on an unexpectedly transformative month in which he launched his consulting business, secured his first two clients, and purchased a new home—all within the same month. Despite being someone who prefers careful planning, he chose to embrace uncertainty instead of trying to control every outcome. He shares how accepting the chaos helped him navigate fear and ultimately led to personal and professional growth.

